        <embedded/>
        <type name="CMIF_BookingRefItem"/>
        <access>protected</access>
        <text>
07/09/2010 - cnwcs5
This property is used differently depending  on whether we are maintaining '
a single or multi line booking.  For a single line booking it is the single 
booking itemand it's values are set from tblExtra.

For a multi line booking it is the item currently being edited (using seperate 
form) and it gets set/reset as the user maintains different items.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
